{"tid":405540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩具不再！玩具反斗城傳最快今日遞交破產申請","createTime":"2017-09-19T02:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T08:56:11.000Z","uid":40152,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcbd03b2c7423731e29e0edad6a050eacf78f7b8","tid":405540,"uid":40152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"早前曾傳出面臨結業危機的玩具反斗城（Toys&quot;R&quot;Us），《彭博》最新再引述知情人士指，玩具反斗城最快今日遞交破產申請。<br />\n外電《CNBC》月初曾引述消息表示，玩具反斗城明年約有4億美元債務到期，現正聘請擅長債務重組的Kirkland &amp; Ellis律師事務所協助，而進入破產程序或為其中一個考慮方案。<br />\n受破產消息影響，玩具生產商美泰兒(Mattel)昨晚美股股價急挫6.24%，創7周以來最大升幅，Hasbro美股股價亦跌1.7%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170919/s00002/1505784933344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170919%2Fs00002%2F1505784933344&d=tiMyvAb75PrcKJvUbSoeUMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=66fe69ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170919%2Fs00002%2F1505784933344&h=ac595bfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170919/s00002/1505784933344</a>"},{"pid":"03a427a42fd108a3d6454777514a05a68a6350ff","tid":405540,"uid":4683,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:39:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾黎 賣d玩具又貴"},{"pid":"f5ba54ab6f5ac37a5a33f0129022f76f2b376271","tid":405540,"uid":2372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:40:14.000Z","msg":"點解間野可以生存咁耐"},{"pid":"1f95bf38e0bfd87e5ee06f2b402618169d474f41","tid":405540,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"等清貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5245a9131deb518e780b4b0cd2c21367c15839","tid":405540,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"冇囡囡figure賣<br />\n邊有大叔幫襯<br />\n抵佢執<br